### Create an uppercase task
POST http://localhost:8080/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "uppercase",
  "data": {
    "text": "hello world"
  }
}

### Create a sum task
POST http://localhost:8080/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "sum",
  "data": {
    "numbers": [
      1,
      2,
      3,
      4,
      5
    ]
  }
}

### Create a generic task (unknown action)
POST http://localhost:8080/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "cleanup",
  "data": {
    "target": "/tmp"
  }
}

### Create multiple tasks rapidly (2 concurrent workers)
POST http://localhost:8080/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "uppercase",
  "data": {
    "text": "task alpha"
  }
}

### Second concurrent task
POST http://localhost:8080/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "sum",
  "data": {
    "numbers": [
      10,
      20,
      30
    ]
  }
}

### Third concurrent task
POST http://localhost:8080/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "uppercase",
  "data": {
    "text": "task gamma"
  }
}

### List all tasks
GET http://localhost:8080/tasks

### List only completed tasks
GET http://localhost:8080/tasks?status=completed

### --- Error cases ---

### Missing action field
POST http://localhost:8080/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "data": {
    "text": "no action"
  }
}

### Invalid JSON
POST http://localhost:8080/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

not-json
